Cecilia Hart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cecilia_Hart 0 Cecilia Hart (February 19, 1948 – October 16, 2016), sometimes credited as Ceci Jones, was an American television and stage actress. Hart is best known for her role as Stacey Erickson in the CBS police drama Paris, which originally ran from 1979 until 1980. Hart co-starred with her future husband James Earl Jones in the series.
